text: Absalyamovo (, ) is a village in Mansurovsky Selsoviet, Uchalinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 89 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == The village is located 89 km from Uchaly and 10 km from Abzakovo. == Ethnicity == The village is inhabited by Bashkirs. == References == Category:Rural localities in Uchalinsky District
title: Absalyamovo, Uchalinsky District, Bashkortostan
